Usage: verifyWellAntenna [-help] [-changeToNotProtect <string>]
                         [-changeToProtect <string>] [-needToProtect <string>] [-report <string> [-detailed ]]

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
-changeToNotProtect <string>     # Specify the cell names that is changed as
                                 # not protection cell (string, optional)
-changeToProtect <string>        # Specify the cell names that is changed as
                                 # protection cell (string, optional)
-detailed                        # report all [CORE|ENDCAP] cells protect
                                 # information in report file (bool, optional)
-needToProtect <string>          # Specify the cell names that need protection
                                 # (string, optional)
-report <string>                 # Specify the report file name
                                 # (string, optional)